humanMachineDialogue.text: The 'pT2(mult)NO(sn)LOVORO' portion of the diagnosis indicates that the tumor is T2 (size between 2-5 cm), there are multiple tumors, no cancer was found in the lymph nodes (N0), there is no evidence of cancer in the soft tissues surrounding the tumor (NO(sn)), and the lymphovascular invasion is lateral or outside of the primary tumor (LOVORO).
